This paper discusses the security and management of networked devices, which falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI) and cybersecurity (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the use of a distributed ledger, which falls under the category of distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). The paper also discusses the use of a configuration management system, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE) and distributed systems (cs.DS). Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.CR and cs.NI, followed by cs.DC, cs.SE, and cs.DS.
